{"tid":2357523,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"近期一定要學識嘅溝女開場白","createTime":"2021-01-07T13:00:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T13:54:48.000Z","uid":23655,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"776f73bd54d56dfc50a6174a77c635f6dc899365","tid":2357523,"uid":23655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T13:00:19.000Z","msg":"相信大家都會為如何結識異性感困惑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多時跟本打開唔到話夾子<br />\n就算就話題都幾句傾完<br />\n而家我就教大家一個好嘅開場白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">喂！你有冇睇連登個眼帶賤種？<br />\n我有幫手推po架</span></span><br />\n咪話我唔教精大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n淨係數臭佢都夠講幾粒鐘<br />\n女人最鍾意比較 大家又可以用佢做反面例子黎襯托自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再一齊追po等料 又係一個互動嘅機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n包大家三日都傾唔哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bdf5e5c364bed0aa2f89777ece255f82c9bfe15","tid":2357523,"uid":389319,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T13:01:23.000Z","msg":"樓主溝女好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1999c97f2c5b6825711b50b5050895eadb8b6b15","tid":2357523,"uid":23655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bdf5e5c364bed0aa2f89777ece255f82c9bfe15","tid":2357523,"uid":389319,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T13:01:23.000Z","msg":"樓主溝女好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T13:03:01.000Z","msg":"我近排幾條新女都係咁r返黎"},{"pid":"e03d3396a9a61d8aafd54e301801052c2b5217a4","tid":2357523,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T13:04:22.000Z","msg":"得左<br />\nThx 🙏"},{"pid":"1ee13a09abb0d832dfd78490186e1d082720a52f","tid":235